---
import SectionLabel from "./SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="px-6 py-20 sm:px-10 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[72rem]">
    <SectionLabel number="00" label="About" />

    <div class="mt-10 grid items-start gap-10 md:grid-cols-[240px_1fr]">
      <div class="relative">
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border-strong bg-bg-elev-2 shadow-[0_8px_30px_-12px_rgba(31,24,19,0.18)]"
          style="transform: rotate(-1deg);"
        >
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/avatar.jpg" type="image/jpeg" />
            <img
              src="/avatar.svg"
              alt="Tyler Dobson"
              width="240"
              height="240"
              loading="lazy"
              class="block h-auto w-full"
            />
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2
          class="font-light tracking-tight text-text"
          style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);"
        >
          Hi, I'm Tyler.
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-text-dim sm:text-lg">
          I'm an undergraduate at the University of South Florida studying Artificial
          Intelligence, Analytics & Information Systems. I build practical AI-powered systems —
          the kind that turn manual workflows into infrastructure that actually runs. My current
          flagship is a multi-agent job application automation system that's running my own
          search on autopilot.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-text-dim sm:text-lg">
          Outside the codebase, I work part-time in event operations with Oak View Group and
          Legends Global, supporting 15,000–20,000+ attendee events across Tampa and
          Philadelphia. It's where I learned that high-pressure execution and clean systems are
          the same skill in different clothes.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="/resume.pdf"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border-strong bg-bg-elev px-4 py-2 text-sm text-text hover:text-accent hover:border-accent transition-all duration-200 ease-out"
          >
            View résumé <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#flagship"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-text-dim hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            See the flagship project <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
